{
  "stem": "6195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the same time, my mind was working like-- it was split in two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do I get out, now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hope it's still pouring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But who is that woman?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As we came closer to each other, she said, Syda?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, Mimi!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was my cousin's wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was a Viennese-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 100% Aryan type, so she wanted to live on the-- I gave you the list, and she's there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they caught her, and brought her to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But because she spoke German, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she was the typist in the office, in a [GERMAN] administration office.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she-- not-- she wasn't typing the confidential stuff, only the everyday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I told her, quickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, do you think he will would put me on the list?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, well, he usually-- in a case like that, he asks me if I know someone that I care for.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if he does-- and she-- he did, and that was just pure lucky.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, Mimi, how do I get out of here?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] It's not pouring like it did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she scribbled and gave an SS man to sign it-- a woman or whoever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't follow her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I was frightened stiff, I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We'll break there, for the end of the tape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
